{"tid":2390572,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"封區漏洞出現 ！ 10歲少女獲酌情處理准離開","createTime":"2021-02-01T15:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T16:26:26.000Z","uid":5195,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"14da0a8d2d6eb3b2ca15198b242139b528e00f3f","tid":2390572,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T15:30:10.000Z","msg":"有母親帶10歲女兒到金鑾大廈一間髮型屋剪髮，其間母親一度離開，至折返時大廈已被封，女兒被困在內。母親表示由封區至晚上10時一直在髮型屋樓下守候，仍無法接觸女兒。<br />\n<br />\n有人員建議為其女兒租住賓館一晚，她怒道：「你哋自己諗吓尖沙嘴嗰啲賓館啦，你哋自己都唔會住啦！」直斥當局「畀我嘅所有offer都係廢」。至晚上10時半，有人員向吳小姐表示得到上級許可酌情處理，容許該名10歲女童完成檢測後離開封鎖區。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同武肺deal好左"},{"pid":"355b249cc84262eb4a17e40e01e63d32ea97d592","tid":2390572,"uid":228955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T15:31:51.000Z","msg":"比人屌咪有酌情處理囉黑警死垃圾"},{"pid":"fca32bfe1ae14b671bb53267068b598658e18fbd","tid":2390572,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T15:32:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2OzO5FA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2OzO5FA.gif&h=a1818429&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58104267054d91c37baae586920c3b8925f9230b","tid":2390572,"uid":130177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T15:34:56.000Z","msg":"外賣仔呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17dcd8811a0fcac7790516c016fbe104ae7c2682","tid":2390572,"uid":29093,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T15:34:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">其後 母親因疏忽照顧兒童被黑狗拘捕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5eff252d040090fc248c49727337